Use the standard library
This is how to cycpattern_check of a and b:
   Remember that n is a's length
   Remember that m is b's length
   Remember that i is 0

   Do this n times:
      Remember that ok is yes
      Remember that j is 0

      Do this m times:
         Remember that k is remainder of (sum of i and j) and n
         When item k in a is not item j in b, then:
            Remember that ok is no
            Leave the loop
         End when
         Increase j
      End do

      When ok is yes, then:
         The answer is 1
      End when

      Increase i
   End do

   The answer is 0
